"{\n  \"judgement\": \"The view that children should be treated with respect and kindness, not as servants or slaves, is more defensible than the blanket claim that all parents who order their children around are abusive.\",\n  \"steering\": \"It's great to see so many people sharing their experiences and perspectives on this. Maybe we can all learn from each other and find ways to communicate more effectively with our kids. What are some strategies that have worked for you in teaching your kids good manners and respect?\"}"